title: Deer Hunter 2: Extended Season
description:
Requires: original Deer Hunter 2 game

If you're searching for that record-book buck, you'll find it with Extended Season, add-on to the top-seller Deer Hunter 2. Use the buck-bustin' tactics you find in the companion book to track your elusive quarry in one of the scenic new locations, searching for the prize monster whitetail or mule deer. Then grab your gear, ready your shotgun, and hop in your truck for a hunt through the rugged terrain of Extended Season, hot on the trail of the largest rack in the woods. It's buck fever all over again, and this time, the biggest game of all is just one shot away.
